room_title: Escape room "Virus" by Optimal Escape in Evansville
room_description:
You and your team have been captured inside the deepest laboratory of a research and experimental facility. You wake up in the quarantine cell and realize you have been infected with a deadly virus. You soon realize you and your team are alone.
Everyone has evacuated the facility and left you to die. You have 60 minutes to find the antidote before the virus acts and kills all of you.
